originalText.text:
I met with Mary who was knowledgeable, friendly, kind and open. She listened to everything I had to say, provided guidance along the way, and quickly figured out a plan of attack for getting my mental health issues under control.

The supporting staff at Carnegie Hill are also so nice and friendly, and always trying to solve problems quickly and effectively.

Such a great practice overall. Highly recommend.

originalText.text: I reached out to Carnegie Hill Psychiatry as I was experiencing severe depression even with my medication. I was linked to Yeqi Chen who was very kind and compassionate in listening to me. She adjusted my medication and recommended some CBT therapy which I have already booked. I am happy with my experience so far and am willing to take the steps into taking care of me and my mental health.

originalText.text: I am so grateful to have found Dr. Tiell! Absolutely wonderful, takes time to get to know her client and gives hope. The office communication is outstanding as well. From signing up for sessions, to a thorough explanation of billing to follow-up after appointments, this is top tier medical service.

originalText.text: I had my first appointment with Carnegie Hill Psychiatry on October 5th and the psychiatrist I spoke with made me feel comfortable immediately and really listened to all of my needs and concerns and gave great feedback. I can not wait to continue on this journey of healing and becoming the best version of myself with their help. If you are looking for a psychiatrist and came across Carnegie Hill look no further. They are patient kind and extremely informative and thorough.
